latestIgtvVideos.title: Easy DIY face mask for that picture perfect glow🌟
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
None of us are doing our regular skincare routine at the moment. We are all adjusting it as per our needs indoors.
So in the next few videos we’ll see skin care and beauty tips in the times of quarantine.💜
.
.
.
Ingredients: Banana🍌Orange🍊Honey🍯
.
(This is suitable for normal to oily skin
People with dry skin should avoid adding the oranges)
.
.
Steps: 
1. Mash half a banana, add 1tbsp orange juice and 1 tbsp honey ( mix it all together)
2. Wash your face and dry well before application.
3. Apply the mask on your face(lumps are totally fine!) Keep the mixture on for 10-15 mins.
4. Rinse with luke warm water and moisturize.
.
.
Extra Instructions:
1)Please donot stretch your face while you have your mask on
2)People with dry skin should avoid adding the oranges.
.
.
.
.
.
.
